title: C_0034_BA9
extract_protocol_ch1.1: Illumina TruSeq RNA Sample Prep Kit, mRNA
data_processing: Bases were called with the Illumina CASAVA 1.7 pipeline
data_processing.1: mRNA-Seq reads were aligned against UCSC hg19 genome build with STAR 2.5.3, parameters --runThreadN 8 --runMode alignReads --readFilesCommand zcat --outSAMtype BAM Unsorted
data_processing.2: Aligned reads were counted against the Gencode v25 annotation gtf using Salmon 0.8.2
data_processing.3: Genes were filtered from further analysis that had more than half of both HD and Control samples with zero counts
data_processing.4: Outlier sample counts in individual genes were filtered
data_processing.5: Differential expression between HD and Control was assessed using DESeq2 v1.3.34
data_processing.7: Supplementary_files_format_and_content: processed file contains normalized counts for all samples
